  <features>
      <feature>Simple 1-finger, 4-direction swipe control</feature>
      <feature>3 glittering, colored bubbles to pop to get past each level, easy!</feature>
      <feature>10 types of creatures, read their move patterns to avoid being checkmated!</feature>
      <feature>13 achievements: start your career as a secret agent octopus</feature>
      <feature>31 different pixelart beetles waiting for your rescue</feature>
      <feature>60 timeless levels, no turn limit either: a pure brainpower game</feature>
      <feature>Cartoonish characters; contains only mild cartoon violence (vanishing creatures)</feature>
      <feature>Freemium model: removable ads, no extra in-app products</feature>
      <feature>Ad-free web playable demo available for html5 browsers including mobile browsers</feature>
  </features>

